{"tid":1192123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"激進派有本事就自己發起號召，唔好破壞民陣既和平遊行","createTime":"2019-06-08T09:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T13:14:49.000Z","uid":222614,"like":10,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8edab893ec69150feee3629e471905149a93b19f","tid":1192123,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"講左幾多次遊行一定要和平，做畀美國睇等佢制裁政府<br />\n<br />\n搞其他乜野佔領衝擊只會折外生枝<br />\n<br />\n你地有本事既就自己發起號召，唔好係度抽水！"},{"pid":"be2603520230bbd8ebcca39b359a45e1ba0ee98c","tid":1192123,"uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:22:48.000Z","msg":"假設如果你想衝但面對人地係和理非嘅立場，唔好鬧人，相反如果你係和理非但面對人地係想衝嘅立場，亦都唔好鬧人甚至阻人，否則會破壞大家關係從而削弱反共力量，所以泛民亦冇必要少少野就玩篤灰破壞自己勢力，<span style=\"color: gold;\">不過我相信大家係為咗反送中呢個目的而唔係為民陣而上街嘅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a6011d0edee85c13e2251fd40532fd72495bf1","tid":1192123,"uid":222614,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:24:54.000Z","msg":"你地係咪要搞到民陣取消遊行先安落？"},{"pid":"58e2eb268555d7edd8a57ddd8fea7e33f728c876","tid":1192123,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcb4fc80b3def8eb03a3d506ee385a3361824c4","tid":1192123,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:26:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為對付三毛無盡攻勢 請大家推爆呢個post 唔好比三毛分化post洗走d集個post</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/10\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/10</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"029dbfca8d002e549176c71eea6e668007834124","tid":1192123,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8edab893ec69150feee3629e471905149a93b19f","tid":1192123,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"講左幾多次遊行一定要和平，做畀美國睇等佢制裁政府<br />\n<br />\n搞其他乜野佔領衝擊只會折外生枝<br />\n<br />\n你地有本事既就自己發起號召，唔好係度抽水！